                                                p Enhanced a proactive issue resolution pipeline within the navigation data to reduce incidence of customers feedback pertaining to navigation.
                                                p Forwarded major tool improvements that increased Streets Review, Mapbox Contribute, Navigation Feedback teams productivity.
                                                
                                                h5 Vandalism Eradication
                                                p Prevented leaks of inappropriate changes from OSM to Mapbox Streets map using internal false-positive probes to test team performance and attentiveness. Attained an impressive team accuracy score of 98% while also maintaining a stringent data review timeline of one week for published content.
                                                p Improved the review workflow for incoming OSM edits that put an end to a 6-months review backlog. Review rate per team member sky-rocketed from 2&nbsp;000 to 12&nbsp;000 views per day during 1 month. 

                                                h5 Internal & External Data Analysis
                                                p Created and optimised high precision dashboards for tracking KPIs and SLAs. 
                                                p Performed an extensive research on OSM data suitability for navigation services comparing with other navigation service providers.
                                                p Conducted private navigation A/B tests for high priority customers.
                                                p Developed a comprehensive workflow for efficiently triaging incoming issues, distributing them among respective teams, and monitoring teams performance.

                                                h5 Documentation & Education
                                                p Created and implemented documentation for map data production for navigation.
                                                p Educated and trained new team members in OSM data model for top performance.
                                                p Pioneered Mapillary as data source for mapping for navigation.
                                                p Established standards of communication between OSM communities and corporate mapping teams.
                                                p Bridged the gap between corporate and crowdsourcing OSM mapping communities.


